ISLAMABAD, Apr 07 (APP):Senior leader of Pakistan Tehreek-e-Insaf Senator Shibli Faraz on Wednesday expressed deep grief and sorrow over the sad demise of Muhammad Javed Iqbal, brother of senior journalist Haji Hamid Habib and Khalid Khurram.
In a condolence message, Shibli Faraz payed to Almighty Allah to rest the departed soul in eternal peace and grant courage to the bereaved family to bear this loss with fortitude.
